@node requirements "What You Need?"
@{b}Requirements:
@{ub}
Any AMIGA computer (68020 or better recommended)
320 KB (270 KB if sounds off) free Chip memory + 250 KB of any type of memory
Hard Disk with 2.0MB of free space
Mouse and color monitor :)

Tested:
A1200/GVP1230/40Mhz  4MB Fast  2MB Chip  560MB HD  OS3.0 
A500 2.5MB Fast  0.5MB Chip  20MB HD  OS1.3

@endnode

@node installation "How to install?"
@{b}Installation:
@{ub}
Copy the fonts into your fonts: directory and @{"medplayer.library" link med} into
your libs: directory and move the "Cursed Kingdoms" drawer where ever
you want it.

@endnode

@node run "How to run the program?"
@{b}Running the program:
@{ub}
1. Click "Make Assigns" icon
2. Click "CK" Icon
3. The program should start

